      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "POISED (8) has enjoyed a 46-day let-up and switched stables since finishing third over 1100m at Mildura. Best figures when prepared in Victoria stand out in this modest field. Well in after Dalton's claim and should be too good for this lot. ARAKOOLA (1) led for the judge but was a spent force soon after on debut recently over today's journey at Coffs Harbour. Will take a lot from that run and can offer more resistance this time. MR ACCURATE (4) has been safely held in his two runs to date. Comes back in trip which may help. NA HAMAH (7) is back from a five-month spell. Will be better for the run but in a race that lacks depth she could fill a top four spot. The locally trained LAST METAPHOR (9) is facing the starter for the first time. Worth watching for a betting push.",
